{
  "macro_id": "staking.open_stake",
  "domain": "staking",
  "name": "open_stake",
  "inputs": {
    "poolId": { "type": "string", "enum": ["flex", "core", "growth"] },
    "principalCc": { "type": "number", "min": 0, "max": 1000000000 },
    "months": { "type": "number", "min": 1, "max": 60 },
    "autoCompound": { "type": "boolean" },
    "liquidReceipt": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || (output.result && typeof output.result.position === 'object' && output.result.position !== null)",
    "output.ok === false || (typeof output.result.position.id === 'string' && output.result.position.id.length > 0)",
    "output.ok === false || (typeof output.result.position.principalCc === 'number' && Number.isFinite(output.result.position.principalCc) && output.result.position.principalCc >= 0)",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.error === 'string'"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    { "input": {}, "expect": { "ok": false, "error": "missing_months" } },
    { "input": { "poolId": "core", "principalCc": 200, "months": 6 }, "expect": { "ok": true } },
    { "input": { "poolId": "growth", "principalCc": 10, "months": 6 }, "expect": { "ok": false } },
    { "input": { "poolId": "core", "principalCc": 1e308, "months": 6 }, "expect": { "ok": false, "error": "invalid_principalCc" } },
    { "input": { "poolId": "core", "principalCc": 100, "months": 1e308 }, "expect": { "ok": false, "error": "invalid_months" } },
    { "input": { "poolId": "nope", "principalCc": 100, "months": 6 }, "expect": { "ok": false, "error": "unknown_pool" } }
  ],
  "_note": "open_stake is a user-scoped WRITE. The assassin runs with an internal owner actor, so it never returns no_actor — {} hits real validation (missing_months). principalCc/months are fail-CLOSED numeric guards via badNumericField: poisoned NaN/Infinity/1e308/negative return ok:false invalid_<field> BEFORE any state write (no Infinity principal can be locked). Below-pool-minimum principal is rejected. State persists in globalThis._concordSTATE.stakingPositions, not a DB — never no_db."
}
